 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of filled areas in the design of layered products.  The areas may be solid filled or filled using curves, hatching, or tiling. Support is provided for predefined and externally defined fill representations.
   </p>
 </purpose>

